				</p>
				
				<div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
						<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
						<p class="font-inter text-light-gray text-sm">All funds deposited directly to your bank account</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
						<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
						<p class="font-inter text-light-gray text-sm">Core component of First Class Merchant system</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
						<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-gold rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
						<p class="font-inter text-light-gray text-sm">Designed specifically for local entrepreneurs and SMEs</p>
